{"tid":2008791,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"踢爆會員 識鬥一定係鬥藍真身乃pprb滲透的警魔","createTime":"2020-05-09T09:41:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-02T04:13:34.000Z","uid":26770,"like":48,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"e290f1e95284998469ce62baad1a62ecdb200c99","tid":2008791,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T09:41:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1980148/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1980148/page/1</a><br />\n一開始扮到好溫和的淺藍扮想同大家溝通<br />\n教你點做<strong>,呢招咪共產黨果招輸出革命導師</strong><br />\n你的一舉一動,下一步做咩自此受呢班人掌握<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2007920/page/14\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2007920/page/14</a><br />\n一開始幫手傳fake news意圖discredit警暴指控<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">遭懷疑下終於發顛侮辱警暴死者</span><br />\n<br />\n其用語就係香港班畜牲警魔的用字, 唔似普通藍絲"},{"pid":"006b8dea8bea532eb23d0228862bd95b9a25cdae","tid":2008791,"uid":202340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T09:44:03.000Z","msg":"又鳩噏"},{"pid":"f29143e3afadd4684a9ddf73fcae7dd688078f63","tid":2008791,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T09:44:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/4nzUThz8BvI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F4nzUThz8BvI&d=i%2FQ10njZfEvfzeNkfPb7d6ix4Ji0%2BaXPUR6dcaOs6Zo%3D&h=b87f8ca5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/4nzUThz8BvI</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/C7YbpoujZlw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FC7YbpoujZlw&d=i%2FQ10njZfEvfzeNkfPb7d6ix4Ji0%2BaXPUR6dcaOs6Zo%3D&h=594c6a52\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/C7YbpoujZlw</a>"},{"pid":"6a96d87cf00b9d34f125e5add5ac652c7051f9d1","tid":2008791,"uid":202340,"like":4,"dislike":11,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T09:45:20.000Z","msg":"拉 樓主老屈其他會員"},{"pid":"0b8d9f90fee0368e2f0229313c6e1f4e1f567540","tid":2008791,"uid":26770,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T09:45:59.000Z","msg":"感謝pprb狗幫手推post"},{"pid":"0d1e3d2aa9132e4f6253f1d88d5e0aa285053e40","tid":2008791,"uid":26770,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T09:57:28.000Z","msg":"pprb先係撥火鬥黃<br />\n跟住老屈黃絲係黃納粹,黃衛兵<br />\n現在睇準議會戰線要35+就扮淺藍革命導師去滲透同誤導<br />\n<br />\n但你們本質就係一班殺人強姦犯<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">點扮去到某個位就會控制唔到情緒自爆<br />\n因你們好清楚一失勢後果一定係終生監禁,壓力大到爆點</span>"},{"pid":"456758abbe7ccc5c85e306ce28a5b78791b7c56f","tid":2008791,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T09:59:50.000Z","msg":"@鳩X冇親戚"},{"pid":"5cc6de4b2bc88fff8d6c6d293923d6bcb9f5f066","tid":2008791,"uid":306914,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T10:01:44.000Z","msg":"留句「港共黑警，時代垃圾」"},{"pid":"c76a5190dbb46333882b3cc3f722d1d52c6903c1","tid":2008791,"uid":44358,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T10:07:27.000Z","msg":"一定有黑警混入連登。"},{"pid":"a544c653c9580c70a01f22eb317b41f6c21f694f","tid":2008791,"uid":26770,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T10:11:40.000Z","msg":"呢班pprb狗最可笑係屈示威者受唔住壓力自殺<br />\n1自殺點解幾分鐘內街坊一到已經現屍斑<br />\n2點解唔公開死者生前搭lift的閉路<br />\n因為死者屍體應該係用電器盒拉上去, 閉路影唔到<br />\n<br />\n無睇過閉路就無資格話係自殺<br />\n 與案無關的警魔, 特別pprb根本無權要求睇證據<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你香港警魔好堅定話示威者自殺已經露底<br />\n因為係你潛意識懷疑乃伙記殺的心理防禦反應</span><br />\n<br />\n唔明就問42樓班仆街,班仆街讀過下屎片應該知"},{"pid":"21218663bb19b3d9eeb168171f795e233be5087a","tid":2008791,"uid":26770,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T10:34:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200305/D7VCG7EKMKXERV4UCUMYYTFGTU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200305%2FD7VCG7EKMKXERV4UCUMYYTFGTU%2F&d=i%2FQ10njZfEvfzeNkfPb7d6ix4Ji0%2BaXPUR6dcaOs6Zo%3D&h=2dcb7100\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200305%2FD7VCG7EKMKXERV4UCUMYYTFGTU%2F&h=12114c48\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200305/D7VCG7EKMKXERV4UCUMYYTFGTU/</a><br />\n<br />\npprb唔止係開狗謊記招<br />\n曾經恐嚇揭露宿者遭群警施暴的林國璋牧師<br />\n<strong>我屌臭班警魔滲透討論區係有根據</strong><br />\n<br />\n知識產權問題只提供節錄,請支持訂閱<br />\n<br />\n[惟記者會後，林牧師便收到警民關係組的來電，稱對記招表示「震驚」，批評記者會是影響警隊形象，並聲言內部確認並無進行類似行動，反問林如何「一口咬定」是警方所為；又要求他在Facebook作澄清及更正，但遭拒絕。]"},{"pid":"143f1c1a53053b698a6cb7e547f3c1b81e0f6b4c","tid":2008791,"uid":57221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T10:43:46.000Z","msg":"pl"},{"pid":"f529dfee0d4fc0390ee4e01ebb4fcbd11c6befb1","tid":2008791,"uid":1581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T10:47:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cf6004efbbe46c64827428a34dc6f14563e721ac","tid":2008791,"uid":47289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T10:51:55.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"7cd7111fce0e613f4784ce325b654c9c619458b1","tid":2008791,"uid":151544,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T11:28:31.000Z","msg":"證據唔太valid <br />\n<br />\n有無多d料？"},{"pid":"9e9fa38e4ed41f23cbe944d0471ec23ff27ee5f6","tid":2008791,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c76a5190dbb46333882b3cc3f722d1d52c6903c1","tid":2008791,"uid":44358,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T10:07:27.000Z","msg":"一定有黑警混入連登。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T11:36:29.000Z","msg":"好撚多<br />\n起碼成team人帶風向"},{"pid":"cda84692f3a0e729d6b5e71b41d1bb66f5a6c674","tid":2008791,"uid":26770,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"7cd7111fce0e613f4784ce325b654c9c619458b1","tid":2008791,"uid":151544,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T11:28:31.000Z","msg":"證據唔太valid <br />\n<br />\n有無多d料？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T12:00:07.000Z","msg":"涉嫌果幾個會員消失左, 連帳號都放棄埋<br />\n<br />\n而呢種事情過去唔止一次,一定有大型組織係幕後推動"},{"pid":"b76c186a0d9adca97730a98ae1fef9e68eaae